Text: As US Representative, I will work to reform DACA and eliminate inhumane processing of illegal immigrants while providing for enforcement of US immigration laws.
U.S. religious freedom must always be preserved.
Affordable healthcare is not available for many Americans. We must continue access to emergency medical services for all citizens of the United States. The economy needs attention now.
